Text: Roseville IDASH Cc Attached is I hope the final IDASH for the Roseville project The only changes are in the return section based on changes to the model requested by Finance Our goal is still to get this signed tomorrow Wednesday Thanks for your patience Mark

Final Roseville IDASH Cc Please find attached the final version of the Roseville IDASH as well as a version redlined against the document sent out yesterday Our plan is to have Ron Coker circulate the document for signature tomorrow Please call if you have any questions Mark

Roseville IDASH Cc Attached is the Roseville IDASH for your review Please provide your comments or changes if any by the end of Tuesday Barring any significant changes we expect to circulate the IDASH for signature on Wednesday The full DASH is in final draft form and will be circulated for your review within the next two weeks Thanks Mark
